ass_list":["post-8141","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-faith-iman","tag-blessing-al-barakah","tag-fiqh","tag-greetings-al-tahyah","tag-manners-adab","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-muhammad","tag-peace-al-salam","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-al-quran","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-al-tashahhud","tag-teaching-al-taleem"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-27j","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":2067,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/11\/tashahhud-sitting-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":8141,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say when sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: While praying behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, we were saying, \u201cPeace be upon Allah, peace be upon this person.\u201d The Prophet told us one day, \"Verily, Allah Himself is Peace. When one of you sits in prayer, let him say,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/what-to-say-final-tashahhud\/","url_meta":{"origin":8141,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say at end of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn \u2018Urjah reported: We asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how do we send blessings upon you and the people of the house? Allah has taught us how to send peace upon you.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: O Allah, send grace upon Muhammad and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/tashahhud-fi-hajjah\/","url_meta":{"origin":8141,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Testifying to faith in prayer and in need","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught us to bear witness to faith in prayer and to bear witness to faith in times of need. Bearing witness in prayer is to say, \u201cGreetings are for Allah, as are prayers and pure things.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3416,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/23\/bless-muhammad-once-ten\/","url_meta":{"origin":8141,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Bless the Prophet once, Allah blesses you ten times","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sends blessings upon me once, Allah will send blessings upon him ten times.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 408 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644